T02TD3424E:86b-1: padma narte shva ra s'a dha nam /
T02TD3424E:86b-3: padma gar gyi dbang phyug gi sgrub thabs /
T02TD3424E:86b-4: padma gar gyi dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3424E:86b-5: sngon du gsungs pa'i cho gas stong pa nyid bsgoms te /
T02TD3424E:86b-6: de nas sna tshogs padma la gnas pa'i zla ba'i steng du hr'i:yig dkar po rnam par bsgoms te /
T02TD3424E:86b-7: de yongs su gyur pa las padma gar gyi dbang phyug gi rigs rje btsun 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug gi bdag nyid bsgom par bya ste /
T02TD3424E:86b-8: zhal gcig phyag bco brgyad pa skyil krung phyed pas bzhugs pa /
T02TD3424E:86b-9: 'od dpag tu med pa dang ral pa'i thor tshugs kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD3424E:86b-10: phyag thams cad kyis sna tshogs padma bsnams pa rnal 'byor ma'i tshogs kyis yongs su bskor ba'o //
T02TD3424E:86b-11: lho dang byang phyogs logs na gnas pa'i sgrol ma dang /
T02TD3424E:86b-15: lha'i rgyan dang gos kyis brgyan pa'o //
T02TD3424E:86b-16: de nas sngags bzlas par bya ste /
T02TD3424E:86b-17: aom hr'i:padma na rte shva ra h'um /
T02TD3424E:86b-18: nad la sogs pa nye bar zhi ba'i mthu chen po zhes pa ni padma gar gyi dbang phyug gi sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
